# New&BetterLoot
![New&BetterLootThanksChatGPT](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c080ea788c1d90e3038c11bd65263a0be8213166_0.webp)
## The datapack adds more interesting drops to mobs. 
## Edited loot list for:
### Passive Mobs
_**Passive Mobs: main**_
- chicken - default drops, egg;
- frog - frogspawn;
- fox - berries;
- camel - leather;
- ocelot - leather;
- armadillo - scutes;
- axolotl - fish;
- turtle - scutes, seagrass, egg;
- sniffer - many meat, red and green wool, rare egg;
- bat - membrane;

_**Passive Mobs: villagers**_
- villager - 0-16 emeralds (50% chance), food;
- wandering trader - lead, milk, rare invisibility potion, emeralds;

### Neutral Mobs
- bee - honeycomb;
- goat - mutton, wool, horn;
- polar bear - fish, leather;
- wolf - leather;

### Hostile Mobs
_**Hostile Mobs: undead**_
- zombie villager - flesh, emeralds;
- zombie - flesh, rare head, iron, misc;
- drowned - flesh, rare head, copper, sea misc;
- stray - bones, bone meal, rare skull, tundra misc;
- skeleton - bones, bone meal, rare skull, rare apple;
- bogged - bones, bone meal, rare skull, mushrooms, swamp misc;
- parched - bones, bone meal, rare skull, desert misc;
- husk - flesh, rare head, gold, desert misc, rare golden food;

_**Hostile Mobs: misc**_
- spider - string, cobweb, more eyes;
- cave spider - eyes, more string, cobweb;
- creeper - gunpowder, rare TNT, head;
- silverfish - bone meal, iron nuggets;
- endermite - chorus fruit;
- phantom - membrane, exp. bottle;

_**Hostile Mobs: nether**_
- blaze - more rods;
- piglin - gold ingots, cheap items from trade list;
- piglin brute - netherite scrap, rare armor trims;

_**Hostile Mobs: raiders**_
- pillager - few emeralds;
- vindicator - emeralds;
- evoker - 100% totem, many emeralds, books (some enchanted), papers;
- ravager - saddle, many meat and leather;
- witch - default + 0-5 healing potions, 0-2 harming potions, mushrooms, rare cauldron/brewing stand, random ingredients;

### Utility Mobs
- allay - amethysts;
- copper golem - 0-9 copper ingots;
- iron golem - 0-3 iron blocks, 0-9 ingots;
- snow golem - 0-2 sticks, coal, snowballs;

### Bosses
- ender dragon - head;
- wither - 0-3 skulls, 0-4 soul sand, exp. bottles, nether star;
- warden - sculk misc, echo shards, 100% "silence" armor trim, exp. bottles;


![New&BetterLootThanksChatGPT2](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0a5801b1daaf6a3a311a798a4724491394b95eda_0.webp)
